This file lists people who have written or made
significant contribution to the 'ark' project.

Please take a look at the ChangeLog file for specific
changes by authors, and look into the THANKS file for
people who helped in various ways on this piece of software.

 -=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=--=-=-=-=-=-


A U T H O R S:
==============

* Me - Rocco Carbone <rocco /at/ tecsiel /dot/ it>
  o Idea
  o Design
  o Core base implementation
  o Several plugins (clients and servers for several protocols, sniffers, etc)
  o Testing
  o Documentation
  o Maintainer


* 'bambolina' - Valeria Lorenzetti <valeria.lorenzetti /at/ gmail /dot/ com>
  o the ark-aware administration plugin webadmin, accesible via HTTP protocol, to remotely control other plugins
  o all the stuff related to html
  o patched the libevent to use OpenSSL with ongoing activities for using GNU TLS


* 'rai' - Raimondo Mangione <raimondo_mangione /at/ hotmail /dot/ com>
  o both client and server plugins talking standard UCP protocol

